# Release Notes - v2.4.1 (2026-04-14 05:27 UTC)

- ✨ **Clean & Focused**: We've removed gamification elements to focus purely on your message consolidation experience.
- 🛡️ **Smart Noise Filtering**: New AI-powered detection for Gmail keeps your inbox clean from marketing clutter and noise.
- 🤝 **Reliable Syncing**: Enhanced task merging and per-room locking ensures your data stays consistent without conflicts.
- 🌐 **Unified Workflow**: Standardized message handling across Slack and WhatsApp for a more seamless cross-platform experience.
- 📊 **Filtering Insights**: Now you can see exactly how much noise our AI has filtered out directly in your usage stats.
- ⚡ **Rock-Solid Stability**: Massive under-the-hood improvements to error handling and background tasks for a smoother experience.

